    "Body": "Content Strategist / Writer at Upvest Alexander March 06, 2020 Upvest builds the financial infrastructure of tomorrow, powered by blockchain. We make it incredibly simple for every company to use the benefits of the blockchain via our APIs. Our solution is globally used in more than 80 countries. Our team comes from all over the world (we sponsor visas) and we are based in Berlin, Germany. Job Description We\u2019re looking for a part-time content writer who could assist us in leveraging our content marketing efforts on-premise in Berlin. Broadly speaking, we\u2019re looking to create high-quality content (case studies, whitepapers, industry reports, customer onboarding material) for the asset tokenization space. Thus, an ideal candidate would have already worked with blockchain startups before and would be showing a deep understanding of both financial markets, as well as the technical aspects of blockchain. Your work: Identify trending topics relevant to our target group Setting up an editorial content roadmap to cater to these targets Setting up distribution channels for the content to expand the reach Writing around two short blog posts, one long-form article/content piece per month Your personal profile: Strong proficiency in the English language Exceptional writing and editing skills with extraordinary attention to detail Ability to craft compelling messaging for both technical and non-technical audiences Comprehensive understanding of the blockchain technology Comprehensive understanding of the financial markets Excellent writing, analysis, and research skills Have the authorization to work in Europe Prior experience in unstructured startup dynamics, which rewards proactive and leadership attitude Ability to take direction and absorb information quickly Ability to communicate effectively and work collaboratively with technical teams Your package: 3-month project-based contract with competitive compensation Opportunity for a full-time position thereafter Option to work remotely 50% of your time You will receive personal coaching sessions We have flat hierarchies, you can grow into any role ???????????????????????? Berlin ???????????????????????????????????? Content ", 
